    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へっへ～ん。&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;にゲンコツ喰らってる～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Pfft, seems &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; put you back in your place, eh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うるせーな！　……いつつっ。
あいつ手加減しないで殴りやがって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shut up! ...Owowow! Damn she didn't hold anything back with that punch...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;たんのおっぱいで、浮かれてるおめぇが悪いだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, you sure were having fun with &lt;Rody&gt;'s big melons! It's your fault bad boy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しょ、しょうがねだろ。
あんなおっきいの当たったら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I can't help it! They were literally right in my face!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そったらこっだから、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に怒られるだ。
ええか！　男のロマンは大きさだけでねーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And that's why &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; got angry! Ah, you see... Men's romance is a difficult thing to understand...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;たんがええっちゅーのは、子どもの言う事だ。
本当の男なら、&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;ぐらいのが一番と言うだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You see &lt;Rody&gt; is great to toy around since you are a kid. But true men know girls like &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt; are la crème de la crème!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんで、そんなこと言えんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The hell you trying to get at?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そりゃ、おめぇ、いくらでも、さ………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, you have to get as much as you like of that but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いくらでも？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Get as much of...what?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_061_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いやいや、なんでもねぇーだ。
おらだけの特権を教えてやる義理はねぇだ、うん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, no. It's nothing. You won't have the privilege to learn about this from me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
